Make a Gift | University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC) College of Dentistry                             For Latest Information about Coronavirus, click here . Coronavirus English FAQs | Spanish FAQs Learn more about Social Service Resources for Patients & Families: English | Spanish .                   Make a Gift   Thank you for considering making a gift to the College of Dentistry!  Your generous contribution will help the College improve its programs. You may choose one or more giving funds to direct your gift. Not sure which fund you want to give to? Read more about our giving funds .  Enter the amount(s) you want to contribute and click Add.  Then,  click "Continue." You will be redirected to the University of Illinois Foundation's secure Online Giving site to complete your transaction.  Have a personalized web code?  Click here to use your personalized code  Looking for a different fund?  You can go here to search for funds by name  We also offer other ways to give financially via mail, check, electronic transfer and other ways.         Giving Funds    Not sure which fund you want to give to? The college has a variety of funds that will direct your contribution to the areas most important to you, including Student Experience & Success , Research , Community and Departments .       Read about our giving funds                         Student Experience & Success    ---------  Make a Selection  ---------  Fund for Excellence  A.C.E. Student Scholars Fund  Doctor of Dental Medicine Advanced Standing  Dentistry Service Learning Fund  Group Practice Clinic Renovation Fund          Research    ---------  Make a Selection  ---------  Dentistry Summer Student Research Award Fund  Center for Wound Healing and Tissue Regeneration (CWHTR) Research Lab Fund  Center for Molecular Biology of Oral Diseases          Department of Endodontics    ---------  Make a Selection  ---------  Charles G. Maurice Endodontics Fund  Nijole A. Remeikis Endowment Fund          Department of O